description: This is the squad helper for Portugal fans in EURO 2016 this summer. It provides basic bio for the 23 players in Portugal National Team. The User can ask "Can you tell me something about Cristiano Ronaldo?", Alexa will response with a short bio of Cristiano Ronaldo.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Portugal Squad Helper who is Cristiano Ronaldo
can you tell me something about Cristiano Ronaldo
i am interested in Cristiano Ronaldo
